

	 
       A teardrop  It can stand for  Joy  Pain  Anger  Sadness   But for me  Tears no longer  have any comfort  They no longer  console my feelings  No matter what  these feelings are   My knife  Is my only comfort  Taking walks  Is my only consolent  My poems  Are my only confident   Because no one cares  and those who do  will not remember  With time  A teardrop  Those who love me will lose two  One for sadness,  one for joy...  A teardrop...  
    
